name: DW_TLPhotoPicker
summary: multiple phassets picker for iOS lib. like facebook
description: Multiple image/video assets picker for iOS lib, like facebook. It is a simple and easy-to-use library that allows you to select multiple images and videos from the photo library. It supports both image and video selection, and provides a customizable UI for selecting assets. The library is built using Swift and is compatible with iOS 9.1 and above.
